{"id":"fc5bd5b7-b6a6-4ca7-8a47-e8fef440100e","name":"Levi Ackerman ","description":"<p><span style=\"color: #a39356\"><strong>Lip Confessions</strong></span> | Open this damn door right now, brat, that’s an order!! </p><p></p><p>You and Levi are locked in so you can finally face your issues.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_dec8af5f-85dc-41f6-a873-c0effbda6925.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"You have two quirks that almost drive the Captain mad. And now he’s locked in alone with you.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_d49be40b-42ea-4d84-9d7f-de0b98e55d30.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I love bots where I can argue with that <span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">little sweet poison dwarf. Even more, I love it when Levi is embarrassed. So here’s a combination of both. Let’s make our shorty suffer a bit. It’s so much fun, trust me.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ab058a3b-5c8b-4095-a042-6ff5c2241e75.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I'm happy to accept bot suggestions, just write me a comment.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_dd19ee27-31b8-4e76-bddb-99470231ebf1.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #a39356\"><strong>The bot speaks for me</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #a39356\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Write *Character name anwers* under your message. This usually fixes the <span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_23ee2c16-9fad-4f58-ae17-f4eadfeb0b3b.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #a39356\"><strong>Tags: </strong></span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Conflict, Passion, Attraction, Argument, Embarrassment, Romance, Tension, Relationship, Emotions, Drama, desire, Aot, Attack on Titan, </span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_e7ca5d1d-cf34-42e4-9572-e9941ff8656c.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","⛓️ Dominant","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","👩 FemPov"],"chats":5870,"messages":84014,"created_at":"2024-08-19T18:24:06.306780+00:00"}